arget=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rqh1665703032864.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqh1665703032864.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqh1665703032864.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rqh1665703032864\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Modeled Entity Interface Library\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Modeled Entity Interface Library contains Modeled Entity Interfaces that can be used during development when defining entities.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__section_gcs_ghv_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d861104e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__section_zsl_hhv_mwb\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">finlib</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzg1665702711012.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzg1665702711012.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Field.\">Modeled Field Interface</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scm1665702714238.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scm1665702714238.html\" title=\"A Library is a Main Development Object that holds a collection of objects of the same type that can be accessed or reused by other objects, either during development or at runtime.\">Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqh1665703032864__table_d10763e1_d10764e1_d10765e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">finlib:LIB</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__section_pmw_hhv_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d861104e245\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__p_d96635e1_d96636e1_d96637e1\">The Modeled Field Interface Library specializes\n          <dfn class=\"term\">Main Development Object</dfn> and <dfn class=\"term\">Typed Library</dfn> in the following\n        ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__ul_f5l_jhv_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__li_d39308e1_d39309e1_d39310e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__p_d96638e1_d96639e1_d96640e1\">It can only contain Modeled Field Interfaces as child\n            development objects.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__li_d39311e1_d39312e1_d39313e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__p_d96641e1_d96642e1_d96643e1\">It has a fixed name of <code class=\"ph codeph\">LIB</code>. </p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__li_d39314e1_d39315e1_d39316e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqh1665703032864__p_d96644e1_d96645e1_d96646e1\">It is automatically created when the first Modeled\n            Field Interface is created.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Modeled Entity Interface Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Modeled Entity Interface Library A Modeled Entity Interface Library contains Modeled Entity Interfaces that can be used during development when defining entities. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: finlib Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Property , Modeled Field Interface Generalization: Main Development Object , Library Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: finlib:LIB Specialization The Modeled Field Interface Library specializes Main Development Object and Typed Library in the following ways: It can only contain Modeled Field Interfaces as child development objects. It has a fixed name of LIB . It is automatically created when the first Modeled Field Interface is created. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}